This topic describes how to resolve common issues with Altoros Elasticsearch for VMware Tanzu.

## <a id='S3 storage minio'></a>Minio

If you use Minio as S3 storage for backup, you have to provide MINIO_DOMAIN environment variable to enable DNS style.
Use this domain as s3 endpoint for backup.


## <a id='Updating Elasticsearch cluster with data'></a>Minio

You should be carefull during update of the cluster with indices on in. Please read this https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/6.8/rolling-upgrades.html.
Configure healht check timeout accordinlly.
